{{etymid|ja|hozo}}
{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=irr|ほぞ}}

[[ateji|Ateji]] or [[misspelling]] for uncommon {{ja-r|表%外%字|ひょう%がい%じ|[[off]]-the-[[chart]] [[character]]|pos=in reference to the chart of {{w|Jōyō kanji|official educational kanji}}}} character {{ja-r|枘|ほぞ|[[navel]]|pos=also generic term for something that [[protrude]]s slightly}}. Note that the right half of {{m|ja|柄}} is {{m|ja|丙}}, with a top bar, while the right half of {{m|ja|枘}} is {{m|ja|内}}, without a top bar.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref>
